        "timestamp": "2018-06-07 14:57:42.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nHi Vamshi, Just to keep down on the admin, where you work on two classes in the same package, would you mind submitting the changes in the same review. OK, we don't want to have reviews with huge numbers of classes but conversely having loads of reviews with only 1 or 2 files changed is a big overhead for us.\n\nMaybe as a rule of thumb, for checkstyle work, you could submit all the classes in one package in a review.\n Thanks Liam",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
